{"about_the_game":"Zofia is a first person RPG - Kick, magic, and melee your enemies as a Seeker trying to stop the blight - A dangerous magical corruption that's determined to bend you to its will.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play the campaign solo or co-operatively with 4 players online, or 2 players in local split screen.<br></li><li>Utilize elemental magic based on your surroundings. Create traps or obstacles for your opponents, or use magic to layer your armor or even launch yourself out of danger. Rare magic tomes allow you to further your magical abilities, if you can find some.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/652770/extras/5855ff19903a6813172c3e444bd7372b91b7044c.gif?t=1720045672\" /><br><br></li><li>Use a grapplehook to get high locations, shortcuts, or secrets... Or as a means to board airships!<br></li><li>Create a custom character from 4 different races, each with their own advantages and disadvantages. From the slow but powerful slime-like Tarbies, to the agile and flying Aves... Or maybe the small and nimble Otter-like Common are for you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/652770/extras/characters.png?t=1720045672\" /><br><br></li><li>Build up your Hub base by finding secret treasures.<br></li><li>Take on enemies with a wide variety of weapons, from elemental weapons, firearms, magic medallions, to ancient equipment.<br></li><li>Bosses, quests, and Gods await you... What will you find, Seeker?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/652770/extras/portal.gif?t=1720045672\" /></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The world is changed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/652770/39e24b67790fe442d0cec48bb52557dece9fdcad.jpg"},{"name":"We burn...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.st